template: INSERT INTO airport (ident, type, name, latitude_deg, longitude_deg) VALUES ("{airports_ident}", "{airports_type}", "{airports_name}", {airports_latitude_deg}, {airports_longitude_deg})
description: Insert a new airport with basic location and identity information.

template: INSERT INTO airport (ident, type, name, latitude_deg, longitude_deg, elevation_ft) VALUES ("{airports_ident}", "{airports_type}", "{airports_name}", {airports_latitude_deg}, {airports_longitude_deg}, {airports_elevation_ft})
description: Insert a new airport record including elevation details.
payload_type: string string string float float float

template: INSERT INTO airport (ident, type, name, wikipedia_link, continent) VALUES ("{airports_ident}","{airports_type}", "{airports_name}","{airports_wikipedia_link}","{airports_continent}")
description: Insert a new airport with a Wikipedia link and continent information.

template: INSERT INTO regions (code, name, continent, iso_country, wikipedia_link, keywords) VALUES ("{regions_code}", "{regions_name}", "{regions_continent}", "{regions_iso_country}", "{regions_wikipedia_link}", "{regions_keywords}")
description: Insert a new region including Wikipedia link and keywords.
payload_type: string string string string string string

template: INSERT INTO regions (code, local_code, name, continent, iso_country) VALUES ("{regions_code}", "{regions_local_code}", "{regions_name}", "{regions_continent}", "{regions_iso_country}")
description: Insert a new region with local code and name details.

template: INSERT INTO countries (code, name, continent, keywords) VALUES ("{countries_code}", "{countries_name}", "{countries_continent}", "{countries_keywords}")
description: Insert a new country record with name, continent, and keywords.

template: INSERT INTO countries (code, name, continent) VALUES ("{countries_code}", "{countries_name}", "{countries_continent}")
description: Insert a new country with code, name, and continent.

template: INSERT INTO airport_frequencies (id, airport_ref, airport_ident, type, description, frequency_mhz) VALUES ({airport-frequencies_id}, {airport-frequencies_airport_ref}, "{airport-frequencies_airport_ident}", "{airport-frequencies_type}", "{airport-frequencies_description}", {airport-frequencies_frequency_mhz})
description: Insert a new airport frequency entry with associated details.
payload_type: int int string string string float

template: INSERT INTO runways (airport_ref, airport_ident, length_ft, surface, lighted, closed) VALUES ({runways_airport_ref}, "{runways_airport_ident}", {runways_length_ft}, "{runways_surface}", {runways_lighted}, {runways_closed})
description: Insert a new runway entry for a specific airport.
payload_type: int string int string int int

template: INSERT INTO navaids (id, ident, name, type, frequency_khz, iso_country) VALUES ({navaids_id}, "{navaids_ident}", "{navaids_name}", "{navaids_type}", {navaids_frequency_khz}, "{navaids_iso_country}")
description: Insert a new navigation aid (navaid) with frequency and location details.
payload_type: int string string string int string
